## Protected Route Component

The `ProtectedRoute` component handles authentication and authorization:

```jsx
// Basic protection (any authenticated user)
<ProtectedRoute>
  <MyPage />
</ProtectedRoute>

// Superuser only
<ProtectedRoute requireSuperuser={true}>
  <AdminPage />
</ProtectedRoute>

// Admin only
<ProtectedRoute requireAdmin={true}>
  <AdminPage />
</ProtectedRoute>

// Specific permission
<ProtectedRoute requiredPermission="manage_users">
  <UserManagementPage />
</ProtectedRoute>
```

## Date Formatting

Always use utilities from `utils/dateUtils.js`:

```jsx
import { formatDate, formatRelativeTime, formatDateOnly, isExpired, isExpiringSoon } from '../utils/dateUtils';

// Full datetime
<td>{formatDate(item.created_at)}</td>  // "Dec 24, 2025 14:30:45"

// Relative time
<span>{formatRelativeTime(item.updated_at)}</span>  // "2 hours ago"

// Date only
<span>{formatDateOnly(item.expires_at)}</span>  // "Dec 24, 2025"

// Expiry checking
{isExpired(cert.expires_at) && <Badge bg="danger">Expired</Badge>}
{isExpiringSoon(cert.expires_at, 30) && <Badge bg="warning">Expiring Soon</Badge>}
```

## Theming (components & pages)

Follow **[`frontend-theming.mdc`](frontend-theming.mdc)** for every UI change:

- Prefer Bootstrap + `className` that already respects `index.css` overrides.
- For inline `style`, use **`var(--bs-border-color)`**, **`var(--bs-card-bg)`**, **`var(--bs-body-color)`**, etc. — not `#f8f9fa`, `#dee2e6`, or default Bootstrap blues.
- For charts or React Flow nodes, use **[`utils/chartTheme.js`](../../src/frontend/src/utils/chartTheme.js)** and **[`utils/workflowNodeTheme.js`](../../src/frontend/src/utils/workflowNodeTheme.js)** instead of duplicating palettes.

## Best Practices

1. **Always destructure context values** - `const { selectedProgram } = useProgramFilter();`
2. **Handle loading, error, and empty states** - Every data-fetching component needs all three
3. **Use consistent Badge colors** - Follow severity/status color conventions
4. **Preserve program filter in links** - Pass `program` param when navigating
5. **Use formatDate utilities** - Never use raw `Date` methods or inline formatting
6. **Show meaningful empty states** - Don't just show empty tables
7. **Use Bootstrap grid** - `Row`, `Col` for layouts, `Container fluid` for pages
8. **Debounce search inputs** - Avoid excessive API calls on typing
